he world in this story is a very different place, with China being the sole superpower.
 They're a highly centralized government, known for having very strict rules about what you can do and where you can go. They've managed to completely wipe out hunger, disease and poverty, but only select people are allowed to have children, to reduce the world population to under 100 million. 

ost of the rest of the world has allied itself with China, but in the United States, memories of  freer times remains. There are rumors that the  corrupt ruler of China has been working on a new system to track down and punish people who are outside their system. Chinese geneticists have unlocked a "susceptibility" gene, that makes people listen to commands.  The government has fed nearly everyone gene-modifying liquids, and control them, as an army of drone. People are discarded when they grow old, or unable to work. But there are a few people, who remember the freedom, before the third World War.
